sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CustomersBroker as Message Broker\n(customers topic)
    participant EventConsumer as orders\nCustomerAddressUpdatedConsumer
    participant IdempotencyStore as Idempotency Store\n(processedEvents)
    participant AddressRepo as CustomerAddressRepository

    CustomersBroker->>EventConsumer: CustomerAddressUpdated\n{ addressId, customerId, street, city,\n  postalCode, reference, deleted }

    EventConsumer->>IdempotencyStore: isAlreadyProcessed(eventId)?
    IdempotencyStore-->>EventConsumer: false (new event)

    alt address exists in LRM
        EventConsumer->>AddressRepo: findByAddressId(addressId)
        AddressRepo-->>EventConsumer: CustomerAddress (existing record)
        EventConsumer->>AddressRepo: upsert(updatedAddress)
        Note over AddressRepo: UPDATE — apply new field values\nincluding deleted flag
    else new address
        EventConsumer->>AddressRepo: findByAddressId(addressId)
        AddressRepo-->>EventConsumer: null
        EventConsumer->>AddressRepo: upsert(newAddress)
        Note over AddressRepo: INSERT — new CustomerAddress record
    end

    AddressRepo-->>EventConsumer: ✓ upserted
    EventConsumer->>IdempotencyStore: markProcessed(eventId, TTL=14d)
    EventConsumer-->>CustomersBroker: ACK

    Note over EventConsumer: Redelivery scenario:\nIdempotencyStore returns true → skip processing → ACK
    Note over AddressRepo: deleted=true → address hidden at checkout\n(DELIVERY_ADDRESS_NOT_FOUND guard in UC-ORD-005)
